OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetrol shortage: Mortar    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftanker tailed by           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffuel-seekers               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A tanker driver has told how he was    
OL,6, tailed by about 20 drivers who were    
OL,7, dismayed to discover he was not        
OL,8, transporting petrol.                   
OL,10,FJohnny Anderson, who drives for Weaver 
OL,11,FHaulage, was transporting 44 tonnes of 
OL,12,Fmortar from Bilston, Wolverhampton, to 
OL,13,Fa building site in Northamptonshire.   
OL,15,FWhen he reached his destination, he saw
OL,16,Fa line of traffic backed up behind him.
OL,18,F"The man at the front... actually said 
OL,19,F'You could have stopped and told us you
OL,20,Fweren't a petrol tanker," he said.     
